---
import Detail from "./components/Detail.astro";
---

<section class="px-2" id="FAQ">
  <div
    class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center opacity-0 -translate-y-20 transition-all duration-1000 content-down"
  >
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">Everything you need to know about using NovaTasks</p>
  </div>

  <div
    class="space-y-4 md:mx-auto md:w-2/3 xl:w-1/3 opacity-0 -translate-y-20 transition-all duration-1000 content-down"
  >
    <Detail
      summary="Is NovaTasks free to use?"
      answer="Yes! NovaTasks has a completely free plan with essential features. You can upgrade anytime to unlock advanced functionality."
    />
    <Detail
      summary="Can I sync tasks between devices?"
      answer="Absolutely. Your tasks are synced in real-time across all devices connected to your account."
    />
    <Detail
      summary="Does NovaTasks work offline?"
      answer="Yes, NovaTasks supports offline mode. Your changes will be synced automatically once you're back online."
    />
    <Detail
      summary="How is my data stored and protected?"
      answer="Your data is encrypted and securely stored using industry-standard protocols. We take privacy seriously and never share your tasks or personal information with third parties."
    />
  </div>
</section>
